齖字的基本解释

齖
yá
古同“牙”。

齖字的汉语字典释义

[①]［yá］
［《廣韻》五加切，平麻，疑。］
［《廣韻》吾駕切，去禡，疑。］
(1)齿不平正。
(2)用同“牙”。
(3)见“齖”。

齖字的康熙字典解释

【亥集下】【齒字部】　齖； 康熙笔画：19； 页码：页1532第26
【廣韻】五加切【集韻】牛加切，?音牙。【玉篇】䶥齖，齒不平。　又【集韻】齖齵，齒不正。　又不聽人語曰聱齖。【唐書·元結傳】能學聱齖，保宗而全家。　又【集韻】魚駕切，音訝。齰齖，齒不相值。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［yá］
["Guangyun" five plus cut, flat hemp, doubt. ]
["Guangyun" I drive to cut, go to the 禡, suspicious. ]
(1) Uneven teeth.
(2) Use the same "tooth".

Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words
[Hai Ji 2] [Tooth Word Department] 　齖; Kangxi strokes: 19; Page number: page 1532 26
[Guangyun] Five plus cut [Jiyun] Niu plus cut, sound teeth. [Jade articles] Jiji, uneven teeth.　[Jiyun] 齖齵, teeth are not straight.　I didn't listen to people's words and said 遱齖. 【Tang Shu·Yuan Jie Biography】Able to learn and protect the family and the whole family.　[Jiyun] The fish cuts, the sound is surprised. The teeth are irrelevant.
